data.description: Assumable Loan is  available. Welcome to this stunning ideally situated just a brief 10-minute drive from Fort Huachuca. This residence boasts convenience and scenic beauty with a hiking trail within easy walking distance. Step into modern comfort & security w/ a Ring doorbell and ADT-equipped property. The home is designed for easy living, featuring a range of smart technologies, including a ''smart'' thermostat, newer refrigerator with smart capabilities, skylights, and recessed lighting - all easily controlled via your smartphone. Under-cabinet lighting illuminates the sleek countertops in the kitchen, a cozy fireplace, complemented by the convenience of fruit trees just outside. Marvel at the breathtaking views of the surrounding mountains from multiple vantage points within the house
